## 🎯 The Single Most Important Sentence

If you remember nothing else, remember this for the Care++ section of your interview:

> *"Care++ was a team final-year project with four members and a published IEEE paper. I primarily led the full-stack integration — Spring Boot backend, React web, JWT auth, REST APIs to our Flask AI service. The AI model implementation was a collaborative team effort. We achieved 96.85% classification accuracy combining ResNet50 for medical images, BioBERT for drug-drug interactions, and Llama-3 for clinical summarization within a hybrid Python and Spring Boot microservices architecture."*

Practice this until it flows in 30 seconds without notes.

